[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/sandstorm">Sandstorm</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/sandstorm">Sandstorm</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A five-turn sandstorm is summoned to hurt all combatants except Rock-, Ground-, and Steel-types.</p>